{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.360", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Werte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.600", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor inzwischen fast 50\u00a0Jahren haben wir Sozialdemokraten und unser damaliger Kanzler Willy Brandt das Bundesausbildungsf\u00f6rderungsgesetz eingef\u00fchrt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.440", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr bin ich meiner Partei dankbar."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.200", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es reicht selbstverst\u00e4ndlich nicht aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier im Bundestag den Geist von Willy Brandt nur zu beschw\u00f6ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Handeln sollte diesem Geist stetig gerecht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum haben wir auch in der vergangenen Legislatur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Gohlke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der 25.\u00a0BAf\u00f6G-Novelle die Leistungen f\u00fcr Studierende sowie Sch\u00fclerinnen und Sch\u00fcler deutlich ausgebaut und substanziell verbessert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das waren wieder einmal entscheidende Schritte zu mehr Bildungsgerechtigkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.320", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.680", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wissen Sie hier alle auch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.240", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf Vorschlag und Dr\u00e4ngen der SPD-Fraktion und der SPD als Partei haben wir im Koalitionsvertrag vereinbart, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.120", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es noch in dieser Legislaturperiode eine weitere BAf\u00f6G-Reform geben wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.640", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum freue ich mich ehrlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir die Debatte heute mit einem Antrag der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.560", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also aus der Opposition heraus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.000", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schon einmal beginnen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sage ich ganz ehrlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sympathien f\u00fcr einige Ihrer Vorschl\u00e4ge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.720", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich muss zun\u00e4chst einmal meine Verwunderung \u00fcber die Basis Ihres Antrags zum Ausdruck bringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.800", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Emp\u00f6rung in allen Ehren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen der Linken: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schlagen uns eine Reform der Ausbildungsf\u00f6rderung vor und st\u00fctzen Ihre Argumente munter auf die Ergebnisse der 21.\u00a0Sozialerhebung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das passt nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wieso nicht? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weil der Erhebungszeitraum des Deutschen Studentenwerks das Sommersemester\u00a02016 war. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das 25.\u00a0BAf\u00f6G-\u00c4nderungsgesetz trat aber erst zum Wintersemester\u00a02016/2017 in Kraft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dementsprechend beschreiben die Befunde die Situation unmittelbar vor der letzten Novelle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das l\u00e4sst Ihren Antrag zwar gut gemeint wirken; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.840", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er ist aber leider, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ehrlich gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.960", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schlecht gemacht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.800", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.680", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir werden das BAf\u00f6G in der Gro\u00dfen Koalition reformieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.480", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir den noch in diesem Jahr erwarteten 22.\u00a0Bericht der Bundesregierung zur \u00dcberpr\u00fcfung der Bedarfss\u00e4tze, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.240", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Freibetr\u00e4ge sowie Vomhunderts\u00e4tze und H\u00f6chstbetr\u00e4ge vorliegen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.440", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann k\u00f6nnen wir erstmals die Wirkungen der 25.\u00a0BAf\u00f6G-Novelle und die damit verbundene Einkommens- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Lebenssituation der Studierenden analysieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.320", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann werden wir ein realistisches aktuelles Bild zur Beurteilung der Gesamtlage der Auszubildenden in Deutschland haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dann machen wir uns sofort an die Arbeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollegin Esdar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.880", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Frage oder Bemerkung der Kollegin Gohlke?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.320", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.680", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag haben wir gemeinsam mit der Union verabredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Ausbildungsf\u00f6rderungsgesetz des Bundes auszubauen und die Leistungen deutlich zu verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser gemeinsames Ziel ist es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.120", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die F\u00f6rderbed\u00fcrftigen besser zu erreichen und bis zum Jahr\u00a02021 eine Trendumkehr bei der Anzahl der Gef\u00f6rderten zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6here Einkommensgrenzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Anhebung der Altersgrenzen sowie flexible F\u00f6rderanspr\u00fcche f\u00fcr Teilzeitstudien und Weiterbildungsmaster sind nur einige der sozialdemokratischen Antworten auf die Reform. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.000", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Soziales und politisches Engagement wollen wir zudem st\u00e4rker bei der F\u00f6rderung ber\u00fccksichtigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.280", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro zus\u00e4tzlich f\u00fcr die BAf\u00f6G-Reform im Koalitionsvertrag veranschlagt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um es deutlich zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.320", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die n\u00e4chste BAf\u00f6G-Novelle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.600", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "soll so rechtzeitig kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie noch in der aktuellen Legislatur ihre Wirkung entfalten kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.200", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr werden wir als Sozialdemokratie sorgen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.720", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.560", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir werden das BAf\u00f6G weiter fit f\u00fcr die Zukunft machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir werden als SPD-Fraktion in der Gro\u00dfen Koalition der Motor f\u00fcr die kommende BAf\u00f6G-Reform sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.760", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf k\u00f6nnen auch Sie in der Opposition sich verlassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.680", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.000", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu einer Kurzintervention hat die Kollegin Nicole Gohlke das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}